```plantuml
@startuml ShiftLeftSecurity_traceleft

actor User
participant "CLI Tool (cobra)" as CLI
participant "Text Processor (golang.org/x/text)" as TextProc
participant "System Interaction (golang.org/x/sys)" as Sys
participant "eBPF Handler (gobpf)" as eBPF
participant "File Watcher (fsnotify)" as Watcher

User -> CLI: Execute command with flags
CLI -> TextProc: Process internationalized text\n(Normalize/IDNA/Collation)
TextProc --> CLI: Processed text

CLI -> Sys: Perform system calls\n(Unix/Windows API)
Sys --> CLI: System response

CLI -> eBPF: Load/attach BPF program
eBPF --> CLI: BPF program status

CLI -> Watcher: Monitor filesystem events
Watcher -> CLI: Filesystem event notification

@enduml
```